================================================================================
ABLATION STUDY (similar to Table 6 in paper)
Setup: K=32 clusters, H=8 heads, N=512 keys
       diversity=1.0, target_sparsity=0.85
       averaged over 3 seeds
================================================================================

                 Configuration |   CosSim |        MSE |   Budget |  Δ vs base
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
           Baseline (β=0, γ=0) |   0.4211 |   0.361943 |   18.57% |          —
   Joint K-V only (β=0.5, γ=0) |   0.4179 |   0.369752 |   18.37% |   -0.327pp
Variance boost only (β=0, γ=0.3) |   0.4116 |   0.383390 |   18.01% |   -0.956pp
    Full method (β=0.5, γ=0.3) |   0.4164 |   0.375187 |   18.15% |   -0.471pp
     Aggressive (β=0.5, γ=0.5) |   0.4285 |   0.351038 |   18.91% |   +0.737pp
     V-dominant (β=1.0, γ=0.3) |   0.4272 |   0.356361 |   18.55% |   +0.603pp

Diễn giải:
 - Joint K-V only: chỉ thay đổi clustering, không boost retrieval
 - Variance boost only: chỉ boost retrieve, dùng key-only clustering
 - Full method: kết hợp cả hai
 - Δ pp dương = cải thiện so với baseline

